WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.301
AI is already curating what you see, from news to social media updates.

00:00:05.301 --> 00:00:11.199
Your morning commute might be smoother thanks to AI-powered traffic management.

00:00:11.199 --> 00:00:18.441
And asking your smart assistant for the weather or to play a song is just the tip of the iceberg.

00:00:18.441 --> 00:00:24.862
Behind the scenes, AI is helping doctors diagnose diseases faster and more accurately.

00:00:24.862 --> 00:00:30.984
Online, AI predicts what you'll want to buy next, making shopping more convenient.

00:00:30.984 --> 00:00:37.181
Learning a new skill? AI tutors are personalizing your education like never before.

00:00:37.181 --> 00:00:43.080
Even the products you use are often made with the help of intelligent machines.

00:00:43.080 --> 00:00:50.994
Artificial intelligence isn't just a futuristic concept; it's woven into the fabric of our everyday lives.

